<h2>Verify your email address</h2>

<p>Hi <%= @user.email_address %>,</p>

<p>Thanks for signing up for demucs:r. Click the link below to verify your email address.</p>

<p><%= link_to "Verify my email", verify_email_url(token: @token) %></p>

<p style="color: #888; font-size: 12px;">This link expires in 24 hours. If you didn't create an account you can ignore this email.</p>
